release_body:
`verify_as_json` can now take an optional parameter `deserialize_json_fields` which if True will produce nicer formatted output.

```json
{
    "type": "dictionary",
    "value": "{\"a\": 1, \"b\": 2, \"c\": 3}"
}
```

vs 

```json
{
    "type": "dictionary",
    "value": {
        "a": 1,
        "b": 2,
        "c": 3
    }
}
```
